#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Māghasutta"
msgstr "3. With Māgha"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.47"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.106"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn2.3:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māgho devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ "
"jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, the glorious god Māgha, lighting up the entire Jeta’s "
"Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "sn2.3:1.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho māgho devaputto bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "and addressed the Buddha in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When what is incinerated do you sleep at ease?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.2"
msgid "kiṃsu chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When what is incinerated is there no sorrow?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.3"
msgid "Kissassu ekadhammassa,"
msgstr "What is the one thing"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:2.4"
msgid "vadhaṃ rocesi gotamā”ti."
msgstr "whose killing you approve?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.1"
msgid "“Kodhaṃ chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When anger’s incinerated you sleep at ease."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.2"
msgid "kodhaṃ chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When anger’s incinerated there is no sorrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.3"
msgid "Kodhassa visamūlassa,"
msgstr "Vatrabhū, anger has a poisoned root,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.4"
msgid "madhuraggassa vatrabhū;"
msgstr "and a honey tip."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.5"
msgid "Vadhaṃ ariyā pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "The noble ones praise the slaying of anger,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.3:3.6"
msgid "tañhi chetvā na socatī”ti."
msgstr "for when it’s incinerated there is no sorrow.”"
